    Exception Description
    FunctionException

Package info.ebenoit.ebul.func Description

This package contains various utilities to be used along with function. This includes support for the float primitive type as well as versions of all interfaces capable of rethrowing checked exceptions as runtime exceptions.
Author:
E. Benoît
